column5: Who is the wise guy that ordered all the funny white stuff flying around outside???
Pouring rain here in London.  Dan.
Who is the wise guy that ordered all the funny white stuff flying around outside???  Brrrr....BRRRRRAAAPPPP BRAPPPPPPPPP (soon....)
Yup. It did not make my day seeing all that white stuff on the ground
Guess the winter tires are going on this weekend or next!
Just starting here in the valley. Taking a break inside from yard work and sorting some Quinte walleye gear.
So glad I put the snows on my wife's car last weekend!
Who is the wise guy that ordered all the funny white stuff flying around outside???  One of Santa's elves did---following orders from the boss!!

Got a facebook update from the Town of Gravenhurst today; and they had the colossal audacity and unmitigated gall to use the phrase 'winter wonderland'. It's only October 27. I usually only get sick of that phrase by mid-December.
Unfortunately it's not going to stay for long. I love snow for deer hunting.  Cheers
Who is the wise guy that ordered all the funny white stuff flying around outside???  LOL, we get snow around Thanksgiving sometimes too!
